snippet.title: Best VGM 2154 - Dragon Quest IX - Cross the Fields, Cross the Mountains
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 735 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=myjd1MnZx5Y

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Dragon Quest IX : Sentinels of the Starry Skies (2009)
Cross the Fields, Cross the Mountains
Koichi Sugiyama
